JOHANNESBURG - The festive sales spree it not over - hot on the heels of Black Friday madness, South Africans are cottoning on to the Cyber Monday trend.  Cyber Monday occurs the Monday after Black Friday and sees massive specials and sales on online purchases.  READ: Black Friday on an upward trend in South Africa Black Friday is marked on the first Friday after Thanksgiving each year with huge specials in brick and mortar stores, although an increasing amount on retailers have opted in recent years to offer their Black Friday deals online as well.  TIPS: Protect yourself from Black Friday hackers South Africans - and, sepsifically, South African retailers - have also jumped on the Cyber Monday bandwagon.  eNCA